---
title: Prosciutto, Mushroom & Cheese Spaghetti with Pear Salad
description: There’s a lot to love about this rich bowl of spaghetti. From the savoury prosciutto to the deep meatiness of the mushrooms, to the gooeyness
of the Cheddar cheese. But our favourite part? It’s got to be that it’s on the table in half an hour. That’s our kind of dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prosciutto-mushroom-cheese-spaghetti-bf319d9a.jpg
